Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:38.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,找到答案了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.52,0:00:50.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,把姊姊變回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:53.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,把一切都恢復原來的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:49.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有聯絡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:08.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:12.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:15.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.67,0:03:18.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我和茉莉見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽她說了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊隱瞞的事情 全部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:46.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.08,0:03:48.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我來幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想讓姊姊幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那是我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:07.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:10.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,離開這個城鎮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:18.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:22.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我能相信嗎 依人說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:31.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都重新開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:37.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,要離開這裡了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:43.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:46.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 不過就在最近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:48.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:49.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,挺急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:53.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是我說的 快點離開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:59.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這樣待下去 我或許會阻止你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:06.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你人真好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:12.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是做不到無動於衷地看著某人犧牲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:19.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個孩子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:25.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,回到了日常生活裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:26.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:30.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,做了痛苦的選擇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去姊姊那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.82,0:05:43.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:46.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好問問姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:50.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊是誰？ 我又是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:52.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:11.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:16.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想老師會不會在生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.37,0:06:20.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你這樣和不來上課一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:23.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為今天呢 是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:24.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,特別？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:27.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,空氣很清新
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:30.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以天空比平時都還要藍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:32.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,到了傍晚就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,鮮豔如燃燒似的夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:38.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天啊 謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:47.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:50.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,她說依人回到蒼乃身邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙她款待我法國吐司
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:55.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很甜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:07:00.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,甜得好像和父母有仇一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:01.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:02.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:12.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:13.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.87,0:07:15.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:19.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你什麼都別問我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:20.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:24.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是不能對我說的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:27.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:31.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,別看我這樣 其實我承受力很強的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:37.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到茉莉是夜禍時也很平靜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對蒼乃的事情也很冷靜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,事到如今 沒什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:41.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.23,0:07:46.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,即便如此 也不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:50.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:55.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 那就沒什麼好擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.13,0:08:03.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得這種話我說得出口嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:04.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你能不能多考慮一下別人的心情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:29.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:33.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:35.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我按過門鈴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:40.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,然後然後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:44.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,很久沒來的鬍子紳士 你們猜他說了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.46,0:08:46.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 讓我們點菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.54,0:08:48.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那種事先別管啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:50.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐 猜他說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:54.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然問這裡的料理能不能全部打包帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:09:00.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,奶油烤海鮮 千里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:04.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力草莓凍 麵包蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,體重計最害怕的必殺技
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:06.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在聽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:08.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.48,0:09:11.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:12.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:14.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:15.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:18.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非又是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:22.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,別說了 今天不要提依人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:25.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.71,0:09:26.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:27.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:31.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你們竟然這樣開我玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:32.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:34.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:38.99,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:45.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再來這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:50.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:51.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們要離開這個城鎮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以還是不要見比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:59.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是說你們要搬家了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,要搬去哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:03.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:08.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,過去和回憶都無法達到的遙遠的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:20.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是以海鮮出名的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:26.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不清楚 我只吃過肉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:28.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:31.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,繭子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:34.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我票買好了 準備離開了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:35.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,何時？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:37.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:42.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,剛史
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:44.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:48.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.92,0:10:49.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:51.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又說一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:06.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你什麼都別問我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:09.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼他要說那樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.22,0:11:14.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好像全都被染成了橙色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:21.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺漸漸離我遠去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:25.93,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:32.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:34.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我有點亂發脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那就沒什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:39.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,千里嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:42.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,紗繪也哭了 我在想該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:44.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明天我會道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.39,0:11:49.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒覺得你不用這麼在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:55.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 塔子 你覺得依人怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:56.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:12:02.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像無法理解… 他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:02.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛才也說過 那個名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:09.41,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,名字？ 依人啊 森宮依人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.70,0:12:11.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宮依人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:13.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,同班同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:16.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都翹課拍藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:18.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名 你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:20.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有那樣的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:23.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才也在和千里她們討論這個人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:26.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.85,0:12:28.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人啊 依人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.46,0:12:33.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 這裡還拍過他的照片 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:35.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:40.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.57,0:12:54.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在意的是那個男孩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:56.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:01.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:19.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要來？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:21.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃 小依有一個請求
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:24.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,請教小依更多的折紙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:26.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 就今天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.37,0:13:33.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.13,0:13:37.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:51.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為今天呢 是特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:53.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,到了傍晚就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.00,0:13:55.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,鮮豔如燃燒似的夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:06.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.95,0:14:08.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你什麼都別問我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:57.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.55,0:15:06.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你覺得這個怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:08.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,三顆星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:09.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:13.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 下一個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:17.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:18.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:20.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:23.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:26.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 因為小依是好孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:40.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:41.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,幾種紅色混在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢溶解在天空裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:50.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不會看到相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:54.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就算看起來一樣 但那也都是不一樣的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:00.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:05.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是依人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:07.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宮依人對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:18.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.23,0:16:20.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:31.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你就在這裡吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:33.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:37.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是幽靈 還握著手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:38.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也有影子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:40.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:41.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:45.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,千里 塔子 紗繪都忘記你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都把依人給…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:50.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事明明不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:53.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:00.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你說句話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,回答我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:09.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 下一個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:10.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:13.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再多教我一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:16.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,教小依… 更多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.76,0:17:20.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:22.02,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:24.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明明已經說了是朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:28.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.15,0:17:31.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 我不想和你分開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.32,0:17:37.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一直 一直都想待在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.34,0:17:41.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你要理解 因為小依是好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:43.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想理解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:46.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不想…不想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:52.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要做什麼好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:03.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,明天早上也會去接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.72,0:18:04.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:06.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和小依 和我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.14,0:18:08.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我們三個人一起去學校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:12.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,上課時你就在這裡看藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:13.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,惹老師生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:18.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,下課鐘響後馬上拿著照相機衝向屋頂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:22.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,然後我一臉不耐煩地去叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:24.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能忘記 那些事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:26.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能忘記啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.91,0:18:30.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不管依人如何許願 如何期望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:36.22,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:46.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:04.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,幻影就如夢境般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:09.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,確實存在於那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:15.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但夢醒之後 就會從記憶中慢慢消去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:28.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:34.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我為什麼在哭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:40.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼眼淚止不住
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:53.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就此分別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:56.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在耍什麼帥啊 事到如今了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:19:57.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:19:59.55,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真丟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:01.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係 我不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:06.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣 真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:10.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是和依人兩個人一起決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:13.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,說到那個男孩的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.94,0:20:15.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,臉上就充滿了遲疑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:16.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,至少不要後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:24.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:27.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.78,0:20:30.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:32.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:42.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一個人的我說不定還是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:46.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,剛史
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:50.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個讓人傷腦筋的公主呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:53.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:33.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:42.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,蒼乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:53.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.80,0:23:34.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真是沒有一點孩子樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.21,0:23:37.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,繭子才是 沒半點孩子樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.08,0:23:38.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.20,0:23:39.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:40.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我早就不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.58,0:23:42.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依也早就不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.63,0:23:44.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:45.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:39.26,FBT,NTP,0,0,360,,{\fad(480,480)}夢想之歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:46.02,FBT,NTP,224,0,224,,幽明的交界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.40,0:01:17.92,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}羽根が白く光り 眩しく飛んで行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.25,0:01:24.41,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}心だけ乗せて欲しいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.93,0:01:32.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}冷たい手を伸ばす 届かない…知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:39.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}だけどいま触れたい君に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:46.08,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}懐かしい風には あの頃の舟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.41,0:01:54.72,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}幻が思い出を見せた
